{
  "stem": "11801.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when, when it came time to leave, unfortunately, most of the doors that these people knocked on were closed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this is something that I think about a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It can't have been very long, because I've done this trip many times.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, not from Germany, but I've done similar trips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I seem to remember it took most of the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I, I was in such a-- you know, I, I was so overwhelmed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was so upset that time meant nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was just-- I didn't really care where I was going anymore at that point.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just wanted to go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought I would be able to stay with my brother, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Uh huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then what did happen when you arrived?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we went to this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] place-- whatever it was-- a reception center.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll call it, call it that, because I don't know what else to call it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it was a dispersement center.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a place where the children came, and from there they were dispersed to different places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember we slept in huge dormitories-- enormous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- I think they were nuns who took care of us there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They came at night and felt your bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To see if you were bed wetters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was incredible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was very degrading.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know how long we were there, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was fairly well behaved there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't recall that we had any problems.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I recall that I-- all I remember of that place was that I used to sit, that we used to sit all day.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
